return ['messages'=>['/high-jewellery/'=>'https://eji.com.hk/zh-hant/%e9%ab%98%e7%b4%9a%e7%8f%a0%e5%af%b6/','<p>A group of butterflies fluttering through a glistening rose garden composing a mid-summer ballet.</p>'=>'<p>一群蝴蝶飛舞穿過閃爍的玫瑰園，編織出一場仲夏芭蕾。</p>','<p>A trip to the moon, an elegant 18k gold brooch adorned with La broderie’s hand-embroidered blue butterflies flying towards a dazzling crescent.</p>'=>'<p>來一趟月球之旅。優雅的18K金胸針，與La broderie手工刺繡的藍色蝴蝶，飛向閃耀新月。</p>','<p>Exquisitely understated, add a subtle touch of elegance and nostalgic glamour with this golden embroidery scarf ring made from 18k gold and sapphire.</p>'=>'<p>精緻含蓄，這款由18K金和寶石製成的金色刺繡絲巾環，為您增添一絲優雅與古典魅力。</p>','<p>Fine Jewellery, Lifestyle</p>'=>'<p>高級珠寶， 生活品味</p>','<p>Part of our 30th anniversary project Fine Jewellery, Lifestyle, EJI joined force with embroidery house La broderie to create <em>Ethereal Dream,</em> a collection of hand-embroidered fine jewellery and hair pieces fuse together the craft of jewellery making and an ancient Chinese cultural heritage accentuated by a French flair.</p>'=>'<p>作為EJI三十週年項目的一部分，EJI與刺繡工坊La broderie攜手打造 <em>仲夏•夢</em><em>，</em>一系列手工刺繡精緻珠寶與髮飾，融合了珠寶製作工藝與傳統中國文化，並由法式風情點綴昇華。</p>','<p>Waltzing to their own rhythms, two winged creatures trace an iridescent trail encrusted with precious stones interlacing in the air.</p>'=>'<p>兩隻蝴蝶在空中交織，隨節奏翩翩起舞，留下鑲嵌著珍貴寶石的虹彩軌跡。</p>','Blue Butterfly Moon'=>'藍蝶月光','Etheral dream'=>'仲夏•夢','Fine hair piece'=>'精緻髮飾','Gold Dust'=>'金粉','High Jewellery'=>'高級珠寶','Home'=>'首頁','PAPILLON BALLET​'=>'蝴蝶芭蕾','Showcase'=>'珍品展示','Summer Dance'=>'夏日舞曲','editor-text-editor-1a439c7'=>'<p>精緻含蓄，這款由18K金和寶石製成的金色刺繡絲巾環，為您增添一絲優雅與古典魅力。</p>','editor-text-editor-40f2ede'=>'<p>一群蝴蝶飛舞穿過閃爍的玫瑰園，編織出一場仲夏芭蕾。</p>','editor-text-editor-7d589f6'=>'<p>兩隻蝴蝶在空中交織，隨節奏翩翩起舞，留下鑲嵌著珍貴寶石的虹彩軌跡。</p>','editor-text-editor-a29af42'=>'<p>高級珠寶， 生活品味</p>','editor-text-editor-a6b023d'=>'<p>來一趟月球之旅。優雅的18K金胸針，與La broderie手工刺繡的藍色蝴蝶，飛向閃耀新月。</p>','editor-text-editor-fb6a15c'=>'<p>作為EJI三十週年項目的一部分，EJI與刺繡工坊La broderie攜手打造 <em>仲夏•夢</em><em>，</em>一系列手工刺繡精緻珠寶與髮飾，融合了珠寶製作工藝與傳統中國文化，並由法式風情點綴昇華。</p>','icon-list-text-a4516c8-23ba1e0'=>'高級珠寶','icon-list-text-a4516c8-24b69d8'=>'首頁','icon-list-url-a4516c8-23ba1e0'=>'https://eji.com.hk/zh-hant/%e9%ab%98%e7%b4%9a%e7%8f%a0%e5%af%b6/','title-heading-2c6fdec'=>'仲夏•夢','title-heading-5358dff'=>'精緻髮飾','title-heading-a23d558'=>'金粉','title-heading-c81071e'=>'珍品展示','title-heading-e7c381b'=>'藍蝶月光','title-heading-f7cc6f6'=>'蝴蝶芭蕾','title-heading-facb22c'=>'夏日舞曲']];
